# Copied to dist/ on every build. The @astrojs/cloudflare adapter emits a
# Pages-style layout, but we deploy as a Worker with Static Assets
# (wrangler deploy + main). These must NOT be uploaded as public assets:
#   _worker.js   — the Worker code itself (served via `main`, not assets)
#   _routes.json — Pages-only routing manifest, ignored by the Workers runtime
_worker.js
_routes.json
